{
  "name": "ack-angular-webcam",
  "version": "1.10.0",
  "description": "Angular webcam component. Based on MediaDevices and getUserMedia.js ",
  "main": "dist/index.js",
  "typings": "dist/index.d.ts",
  "scripts": {
    "stats": "webpack-bundle-analyzer example/www/stats.json",
    "stats:html": "webpack-bundle-analyzer example/www/stats.json --mode static --report example/www/stats.html --no-open",
    "build:templates": "ack-pug-bundler example/app example/app --outFileExt template.ts --outType ts --oneToOne",
    "start": "ack-reload -d example/www -b",
    "test:old": "karma start --sr",
    
    "watch:ng": "ng serve example --open",

    "watch:dist": "watch \"npm-run-all build:dist\" src/",
    "watch": "npm-run-all --parallel watch:dist watch:ng watch:templates",
    "watch:templates": "npm run build:templates -- --watch",
    "build:dist": "ngc --declaration --project src",
    "ack-webpack": "ack-webpack",
    "build": "npm-run-all build:templates compile:dist:package build:dist build:example stats",
    "build:example": "ng build example --prod --output-hashing=none --stats-json",
    "_build:js": "node --max-old-space-size=8192 ./node_modules/.bin/ng build --app=example --sourcemaps=true --output-hashing=all",
    "compile:dist:package": "node scripts/update-dist-package.js",
    "test": "ng test --browser PhantomJS --single-run",
    "test:watch": "ng test"
  },
  "repository": {
    "type": "git",
    "url": "git+https://github.com/ackerapple/ack-angular-webcam.git"
  },
  "keywords": [

    "@angular/compiler": "^8.0.0",
    "@angular/compiler-cli": "^8.0.0",
    "@angular/core": "^8.0.0",
    "@angular/platform-browser": "^8.0.0",
    "@angular/platform-browser-dynamic": "^8.0.0",
    "ack-pug-bundler": "^1.4.7",
    "classlist-polyfill": "^1.2.0",
    "codelyzer": "^5.0.1",
    "core-js": "^3.1.3",
    "minimatch": "^3.0.4",
    "npm-run-all": "^4.1.2",
    "reflect-metadata": "^0.1.10",
    "rxjs": "^6.5.2",
    "typescript": "^3.4.5",
    "webpack-bundle-analyzer": "^3.3.2",
    "zone.js": "~0.9.1"
  },

    "url": "https://github.com/ackerapple/ack-angular-webcam/issues"
  },
  "homepage": "https://github.com/ackerapple/ack-angular-webcam#readme",

    "example": "example"
